    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been formally assessed and all meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was not formally assessed on the basis that the validation geometry and operating conditions are judged by the team to be directly representative of the COU, making a formal equivalency evaluation unnecessary. The overall credibility evidence is considered sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
